<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">Welcome to Fakebook</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 12px; font-style: italic;">Find & follow friends, post & chat.</p>

  <p>Hi <span style="font-weight: bold;"><%= @username %></span>, thanks for signing up, it's good to have you here.</p>

  <p>Head over to the users index to make friends and follow <%= link_to "people", users_url %>.</p>
  <p>Posts from those that you're following appear in your <%= link_to "homepage", root_url %>.</p>

  <p>Happy social'ing!</p>

  <p style="font-style: italic;">View and make any required changes to your profile <%= link_to 'here', user_url(@user) %>.</p>
  <%= image_tag attachments['fakebook_logo.png'].url, style: "width: 11px; height: 11px; border-radius: 50%;", alt: "fakebook logo" %>
</body>